QuestData.Title: Volatile Reactions
QuestData.Description:
The living slime within Maldraxxus naturally produces a powerful catalyst used in many of the House of Eyes's poisons. There is always a need for the substance.
It would be of great help if you could retrieve some for us.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa animated catalysts from the slime around Maldraxxus.
QuestData.RewardText: A respectable amount. We will make good use of this.
